'''Dennis Sherman''' (March 29, 1988 - October 11, 2022) was an Australian dentist. 

==Early life==
Dennis was born in Sydney to Aaliyah (born 1961) and Jason Sherman (born 1947). His mother is a receptionist, and his father is a retired trucker.

